kimononet.util

Class ByteManipulation

  • java.lang.Object
    • kimononet.util.ByteManipulation

  • public class ByteManipulation
extends java.lang.Object
    Byte manipulation allows converting Java primitive types into byte arrays and vice versa. However, be careful with the use of this class. It his highly encouraged to use Parcel instead.
    Author:
    Zorayr Khalapyan
